  "Description": {
    "English": "A <span class=\"name name-technology\">biotechnical firewall</span>, developed as a safeguard against textual cognitohazards. It is coated in something slippery, and has started to bubble along the surface.<br><br>Embedded beneath the skin, this grants administrative access to ancient forbidden texts bound at a <span class=\"name name-special\">Planetary Archive</span>.<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">Warning</span>: Do not unbind the forbidden texts. Exposure to forbidden texts carries extreme risk.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "用于避免因文字造成意识损坏的<span class=\"name name-technology\">生物防火墙</span>。外面摸上去滑溜溜的，而且表面已经开始冒泡。<br><br>进行皮下安装之后，这种装置将允许使用者查看<span class=\"name name-special\">行星档案馆</span>中的古代禁忌文本。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：请勿揭示禁忌文字。接触禁忌文字将带来极端威胁！",
    "TraditionalChinese": "一道<span class=\"name name-technology\">生物技術防火牆</span>，被開發用以防止暴露於文本所造成的認知危險。被包覆在某種濕滑物質中，表面已開始冒泡。<br><br>嵌入皮下組織後，能授予<span class=\"name name-special\">星球資料庫</span>古老禁忌文本冊的管理者存取權限。<br><span class=\"name name-fuel\">警告</span>：請勿解開禁忌文本。暴露在禁忌文本之下，會帶來極大風險。"
  },
